
rss2mbox reads urls to RSS-feeds from stdin, fetch them and prints each
article as an htmlized mail in a mbox format to stdout. HTML-rendering
is delegated to the MUA.

USAGE

cat $HOME/.rssfeeds | rss2mbox >> $HOME/.mail/inbox

A tip might be to run it from cron.


REQUIREMENT

 * Python (Known to work with 2.6.1)
 * feedparser <http://www.feedparser.org/>

